title: Derive Debug, Clone, PartialEq, Eq for EraPayoutParams
doc:
- audience: Runtime Dev
  description: |-
    `polkadot_runtime_common::impls::EraPayoutParams` now derives `Debug`, `Clone`,
    `PartialEq` and `Eq`, so runtimes can log and compare the era-payout parameters they
    construct.
crates:
- name: polkadot-runtime-common
  bump: minor
